~sina wile sona e pona tan.
~mi mama sina la
~mi lukin e ken a sina.
~tenpo ni la wawa insa li
~open ala li kama suli.

From this point on, we see SINA in different form singing, switching from between different iterations of SINA. MAMA is shown singing and/or playing the ukulele in their empty space.

