~li ken ala jo e insa sin.
~sina jan ale. sina soweli kin.
~ante la sina ale lon. ni
~li toki pona pona taso.
~ale la mi tu li lon kon laso.

[[hook 2]]

SINA
~mi kama sama sina.
~mi kama mama pi jan
~sama mi sama li pali
~e sike sin mama kin.
~tenpo kama kama la
~pakala e ma ali la
~ijo lon li sama kin
~pi mi en sina.
~    sina li mama mi.

[[verse 3]]

MAMA and SINA are singing face-to-face, SINA finally getting a hunch on what existance is about (though still far from becoming their true self), and accepting their role in it.

MAMA
~mi mama sina. --

SINA
~-- mi jan lili sina.

MAMA & SINA
~insa la mi tu li sama.

MAMA
~tenpo kama la sina sona
~e sona ale pi ma ona.

SINA
~mi wile sona e sona ale.

MAMA
~taso nanpa wan la sina wile
~poka e lon mi la sina ken
~toki e wile ala anu wile.

SINA
~mi wile a! mi wile mute!

MAMA
~sina sona ala e wile.
~sina kama sona e lon ni:
~sona ale li sona suli.
~sona li ken pana e
~pilin apeja e pilin ike.
~tenpo ni la sina ken ala.
~taso tenpo kama la sina wawa.

[[outro]]

SINA
~mi awen la mi sona.

MAMA
~sina awen la mi sona
~e ken sina e wawa sin,
~lon insa sina sama mi.

SINA
~taso lon li apeja.

MAMA
~taso lon li wile a!
~tenpo ni la sina ken ala
~la sina--

SINA drops back down to be reincarnated.

MAMA (CONT'D)
~li tawa monsi.

MAMA sits down once again and begins to hum/whistle a variation of the song's beginning.


